OL,3,CIrish premier 'working towards
OL,4,Creconciliation and mutual trust' in
OL,5,CBelfast visit
OL,7,FIrish premier Micheal Martin has vowed
OL,8,Fto continue working towards
OL,9,Freconciliation and mutual trust ahead
OL,10,Fof a visit to Belfast.
OL,12,FThe Taoiseach is set to meet with
OL,13,Fpolitical leaders at Stormont, as well
OL,14,Fas with business leaders, and engage
OL,15,Fwith Women's Aid.
OL,17,FHe will also mark the signing of a 700
OL,18,Fmillion euro (#604 million) contract
OL,19,Ffor a new fleet of cross border trains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
