OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778119410
OL,3,CIrish premier 'working towards
OL,4,Creconciliation and mutual trust' in
OL,5,CBelfast visit
OL,7,FLater, Mr Martin is to deliver the
OL,8,FLord David Trimble Lecture 2026 at
OL,9,FQueen's University Belfast.
OL,11,FSpeaking ahead of his visit, the
OL,12,FTaoiseach said he is pleased to be
OL,13,Freturning to Belfast.
OL,15,F"My visit includes multiple
OL,16,Fopportunities to hear directly from
OL,17,Fpolitical, business and civic leaders
OL,18,Fand to discuss ongoing and evolving
OL,19,Fall-island priorities which benefit us
OL,20,Fall," he said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU|D@EO]
