OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778119410
OL,3,CIrish premier 'working towards
OL,4,Creconciliation and mutual trust' in
OL,5,CBelfast visit
OL,7,F"I am also pleased to be delivering
OL,8,Fthe Lord David Trimble Lecture in
OL,9,FQueen's University. David played a
OL,10,Fcritical role in the achievement of
OL,11,Fthe Good Friday Agreement.
OL,13,F"The principles and purpose of the
OL,14,FAgreement remain central to what my
OL,15,FGovernment does and how we foster
OL,16,Frelationships across these islands."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@dO]
