OL,3,CIrish premier 'working towards
OL,4,Creconciliation and mutual trust' in
OL,5,CBelfast visit
OL,7,FHe added: "I am committed to
OL,8,Fcontinuing to work toward
OL,9,Freconciliation and mutual trust, as we
OL,10,Fcollectively set out to do in 1998,
OL,11,Fincluding through the Shared Island
OL,12,FInitiative."
